---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="SocialProof vs Broadly — Testimonial Tool Comparison | SocialProof" description="Broadly charges $200+/mo for reputation management. SocialProof is free to start and $9/mo Pro — built for small businesses who just need testimonials." canonical="https://socialproof.dev/vs/broadly">
<style>
    body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; margin: 0; background: #fff; color: #111; }
    nav { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; padding: 1rem 2rem; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; }
    nav a.logo { font-weight: 800; font-size: 1.25rem; color: #111; text-decoration: none; }
    nav .nav-links a { margin-left: 1.5rem; color: #555; text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.95rem; }
    nav .cta-nav { background: #111; color: #fff !important; padding: .45rem 1rem; border-radius: 6px; }
    .hero { text-align: center; padding: 4rem 2rem 2rem; max-width: 760px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .vs-badge { display: inline-block; background: #f0f0f0; color: #555; font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: .06em; text-transform: uppercase; padding: .35rem .75rem; border-radius: 99px; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .hero h1 { font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem); font-weight: 800; line-height: 1.15; margin: 0 0 1rem; }
    .hero h1 span { color: #4f46e5; }
    .hero p { font-size: 1.15rem; color: #444; max-width: 560px; margin: 0 auto 2rem; }
    .hero-cta { display: inline-block; background: #4f46e5; color: #fff; padding: .85rem 2rem; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 700; text-decoration: none; font-size: 1rem; }
    .hero-cta:hover { background: #3730a3; }
    .price-callout { display: inline-flex; gap: 2rem; background: #f9f9f9; border: 1px solid #e5e5e5; border-radius: 12px; padding: 1.25rem 2rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
    .price-callout .item { text-align: center; }
    .price-callout .item .price { font-size: 1.8rem; font-weight: 800; }
    .price-callout .item .label { font-size: 0.85rem; color: #777; margin-top: .2rem; }
    .price-callout .item.vouch .price { color: #4f46e5; }
    .price-callout .item.other .price { color: #dc2626; }
    section { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 3rem 2rem; }
    h2 { font-size: 1.6rem; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
    .compare-table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 2rem 0; }
    .compare-table th { padding: .75rem 1rem; text-align: left; font-size: 0.85rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .05em; color: #888; border-bottom: 2px solid #eee; }
    .compare-table th:nth-child(2) { color: #4f46e5; }
    .compare-table td { padding: .85rem 1rem; border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f0; font-size: 0.97rem; vertical-align: top; }
    .compare-table tr:last-child td { border-bottom: none; }
    .compare-table td:first-child { color: #555; font-weight: 500; }
    .yes { color: #16a34a; font-weight: 600; }
    .no { color: #dc2626; font-weight: 600; }
    .partial { color: #d97706; font-weight: 600; }
    .winner-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 2rem; margin: 2rem 0; }
    .winner-card { border-radius: 12px; padding: 1.75rem; }
    .winner-card.vouch { background: #f0fdf4; border: 1px solid #86efac; }
    .winner-card.other { background: #fafafa; border: 1px solid #e5e5e5; }
    .winner-card h3 { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 800; margin: 0 0 .75rem; }
    .winner-card ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.2rem; }
    .winner-card li { font-size: 0.92rem; color: #444; margin-bottom: .4rem; }
    .savings-box { background: #fffbeb; border: 1px solid #fcd34d; border-radius: 12px; padding: 1.5rem 2rem; margin: 2rem 0; }
    .savings-box h3 { margin: 0 0 .5rem; font-size: 1rem; }
    .savings-box p { margin: 0; color: #555; font-size: 0.95rem; }
    .bottom-cta { text-align: center; background: #f9f9f9; border-top: 1px solid #eee; padding: 4rem 2rem; }
    .bottom-cta h2 { font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .bottom-cta p { color: #555; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
    .cta-btn { display: inline-block; background: #4f46e5; color: #fff; padding: 1rem 2.5rem; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 700; text-decoration: none; font-size: 1.1rem; }
    footer { text-align: center; padding: 2rem; color: #999; font-size: 0.85rem; border-top: 1px solid #eee; }
    footer a { color: #999; }
</style>
<nav>
  <a class="logo" href="/">SocialProof</a>
  <div class="nav-links">
    <a href="/vs/">All Comparisons</a>
    <a href="/#pricing">Pricing</a>
    <a href="https://app.socialproof.dev/register" class="cta-nav">Try free</a>
  </div>
</nav>

<div class="hero">
  <div class="vs-badge">Tool Comparison</div>
  <h1>SocialProof vs <span>Broadly</span></h1>
  <p>Broadly is a full reputation management suite priced for agencies and enterprises. SocialProof is built for small businesses who just need testimonials — simple, affordable, effective.</p>
  <div class="price-callout">
    <div class="item vouch">
      <div class="price">Free</div>
      <div class="label">SocialProof to start</div>
    </div>
    <div class="item other">
      <div class="price">$200+</div>
      <div class="label">Broadly per month</div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <a href="https://app.socialproof.dev/register" class="hero-cta">Start free — no credit card</a>
</div>

<section>
  <h2>Feature comparison</h2>
  <table class="compare-table">
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th>Feature</th>
        <th>SocialProof</th>
        <th>Broadly</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr>
        <td>Starting price</td>
        <td><span class="yes">Free forever for 1 widget</span></td>
        <td><span class="no">~$200+/mo (custom pricing)</span></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Testimonial collection</td>
        <td><span class="yes">✓ Dedicated collection page</span></td>
        <td><span class="yes">✓ Review requests</span></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Embeddable widget</td>
        <td><span class="yes">✓ 1-line embed</span></td>
        <td><span class="partial">✓ Widget available</span></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Built for small business</td>
        <td><span class="yes">✓ Core focus</span></td>
        <td><span class="partial">✗ Enterprise/agency focus</span></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>No credit card to start</td>
        <td><span class="yes">✓</span></td>
        <td><span class="no">✗ Demo required</span></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Google review management</td>
        <td><span class="no">✗ Direct testimonials only</span></td>
        <td><span class="yes">✓ Core feature</span></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>SMS outreach</td>
        <td><span class="no">✗</span></td>
        <td><span class="yes">✓</span></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Simple setup (< 5 min)</td>
        <td><span class="yes">✓ No demo call needed</span></td>
        <td><span class="no">✗ Sales call required</span></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Transparent pricing</td>
        <td><span class="yes">✓ $0 free, $9/mo Pro</span></td>
        <td><span class="no">✗ Custom/opaque</span></td>
      </tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <div class="winner-grid">
    <div class="winner-card vouch">
      <h3>✅ Choose SocialProof if…</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>You're a small business owner, not an enterprise</li>
        <li>You want to collect testimonials without a sales call</li>
        <li>You need something up and running in under 5 minutes</li>
        <li>You can't justify $200+/mo for a testimonial tool</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="winner-card other">
      <h3>Consider Broadly if…</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>You need full reputation management across multiple locations</li>
        <li>You want SMS review requests integrated with your CRM</li>
        <li>Your business manages 10+ locations or franchises</li>
        <li>You have budget for an enterprise-tier platform</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="savings-box">
    <h3>💰 The math is simple</h3>
    <p>Broadly's custom pricing starts well above $200/mo. SocialProof Pro is <strong>$9/mo</strong>. For a small business that just wants testimonials on their website, the choice is clear — and free to try.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="bottom-cta">
  <h2>Testimonials without the enterprise price tag</h2>
  <p>No demo call. No contract. No monthly fee to start. Your customers' words, on your site.</p>
  <a href="https://app.socialproof.dev/register" class="cta-btn">Start free today</a>
</div>

<footer>
  <p>© 2025 SocialProof · <a href="/">Home</a> · <a href="/vs/">All Comparisons</a> · <a href="/#pricing">Pricing</a></p>
</footer>
</Base>
